{"tid":830653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無論咩時間搭東鐵綫都想死","createTime":"2018-09-21T10:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T11:36:34.000Z","uid":125966,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"dcae7cf1e7c7125b5f3038ebad721fff9a459e7d","tid":830653,"uid":125966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:15:34.000Z","msg":"返放工時間就唔再講<br />\n試過晏就兩三點搭出去 都係迫到人貼人<br />\n未到放工時間 五點由九龍塘搭返去<br />\n多喼多蝗仲有成堆打機唔熄聲 播片大大聲既廢老<br />\n拎住一袋二袋戰利品 啲紙袋不停界到人隻腳<br />\n扶住手環既人啲手肘亂鳩咁批<br />\n啲無家教既支那仔 玩口水抹落扶手 衰啲再打落你到<br />\n你睥住佢 佢只會變本加厲<br />\n<br />\n剩底敢怒不敢言既香港人<br />\n每一程東鐵都係折磨<br />\n鬼叫自己窮要住新界<br />\n<br />\n有時候真係好想短十年命<br />\n都想滅絕蝗 唔滅絕都好 禁止佢地再落黎香港<br />\n<br />\n岩先終於搭完返到屋企<br />\n但個內心都係充滿崩潰同絕望<br />\n香港真係好撚細 幾時先逼撚完一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667d54975f827cf9eb068a450beb6272e582bd4a","tid":830653,"uid":77104,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:17:59.000Z","msg":"車尾冇咩人"},{"pid":"823025c6a7f1270672a50ff74d148c70c48308f7","tid":830653,"uid":205844,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"慳果幾十萬住大西北，抵你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cc7eae03592511190eb1d219883515fa54afc8","tid":830653,"uid":125966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"823025c6a7f1270672a50ff74d148c70c48308f7","tid":830653,"uid":205844,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"慳果幾十萬住大西北，抵你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:22:09.000Z","msg":"一出世就住係到<br />\n而家香港人有能力買樓既 一早搬出去<br />\n完全折磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7093a7325358869e8080da9203118b0ef3b647c6","tid":830653,"uid":205844,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b8cc7eae03592511190eb1d219883515fa54afc8","tid":830653